show.description: Usne ek superstar se shaadi ki, fir divorce hua. Sab soch rahe the game over hai. Par usi breakup ne uski zindagi ka reset button daba diya! Yeh story hai James ki . Ek ordinary aadmi se extraordinary banne tak ka asli masaledaar safar. Abhi dekhana shuru kijiye.
